thread.title: BRIEF-Jordan's Mediterranean Tourism Investment FY Profit Falls

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jordan's Mediterranean Tourism Investment FY Profit Falls

organizations.name: mediterranean tourism investment fy profit falls feb

text:
Feb 8 (Reuters) - MEDITERRANEAN TOURISM INVESTMENT COMPANY :
* FY NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO SHAREHOLDERS 2.8 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 3.3 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* FY NET OPERATING REVENUE 5.9 MILLION DINARS VERSUS 6.6 MILLION DINARS YEAR AGO
* BOARD PROPOSES FY CASH DIVIDEND OF 5.5 PERCENT OF SHARE CAPITAL Source: ( bit.ly/2BL3GRD ) Further company coverage: )
